<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FF5A6AE5F82193491814BDD6" pageId="161" pageNumber="923" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFF5A6AE5F82193491814BDD6" blockId="161.[2010,2606,1217,1645]" lastBlockId="161.[1399,2609,1651,3145]" pageId="161" pageNumber="923">
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF5A6AE5F82193491683BE03" authorityName="Ziegler" authorityYear="2003" box="[2013,2179,1296,1329]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Submyotodon" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="161" pageNumber="923" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Submyotodon</taxonomicName>
was originally described based on fossil material. After comparing molars of the extinct type species, S. petersbuchensis, and S. 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF5A6AE5F72E93D61746BE9A" authorityName="Kishida" authorityYear="1932" box="[2258,2374,1423,1448]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Myotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="161" pageNumber="923" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="latirostris">latirostris</taxonomicName>
(then included under 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF5A6AE5F7BA93F7171DBEFD" baseAuthorityName="Gray" baseAuthorityYear="1846" box="[2118,2333,1454,1487]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Myotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="161" pageNumber="923" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="muricola">Myotis muricola</taxonomicName>
as a subspecies), S. 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF5A6AE5F802938C1672BEC4" authorityName="Kishida" authorityYear="1932" box="[2046,2162,1493,1526]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Myotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="161" pageNumber="923" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="latirostris">latirostris</taxonomicName>
and two taxa previously considered subspecies of 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF5A6AE5F71693A41788BD2C" baseAuthorityName="Gray" baseAuthorityYear="1846" box="[2282,2440,1533,1566]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Myotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="161" pageNumber="923" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="muricola">M. muricola</taxonomicName>
(
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF5A6AE5F66293A4142DBD2C" authorityName="Tomes" authorityYear="1859" box="[2462,2605,1533,1566]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Vespertilio" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="161" pageNumber="923" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="caliginosus">caliginosus</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF5A6AE5F7E2907D16BBBD77" authorityName="MilneEdwards" authorityYear="1872" box="[2078,2235,1572,1605]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Vespertilio" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="161" pageNumber="923" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="moupinensis">moupinensis</taxonomicName>
) were moved to 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF5A6AE5F653907D160EBD5F" authorityName="Ziegler" authorityYear="2003" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Submyotodon" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="161" pageNumber="923" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Submyotodon</taxonomicName>
. The genus issister to the rest of 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF5A6AE5F61490091BBEBDA6" authorityName="Tate" authorityYear="1942" pageId="161" pageNumber="835" rank="subFamily" subFamily="Myotinae">Myotinae</taxonomicName>
, except for Fudiscopus (somewhat tentatively in 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF5A6AE5F79D902A16EABDA6" authorityName="Tate" authorityYear="1942" box="[2145,2282,1651,1684]" pageId="161" pageNumber="835" rank="subFamily" subFamily="Myotinae">Myotinae</taxonomicName>
). Relationships among S. 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF5A6AE5FA6090C21810BD8E" authorityName="Kishida" authorityYear="1932" box="[1436,1552,1691,1724]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Myotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="161" pageNumber="923" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="latirostris">latirostris</taxonomicName>
, S. 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF5A6AE5F9B890C218D0BD8E" authorityName="Tomes" authorityYear="1859" box="[1604,1744,1691,1724]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Vespertilio" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="161" pageNumber="923" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="caliginosus">caliginosus</taxonomicName>
, and S. 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF5A6AE5F8BA90C219E2BD8E" authorityName="MilneEdwards" authorityYear="1872" box="[1862,2018,1691,1724]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Vespertilio" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="161" pageNumber="923" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="moupinensis">moupinensis</taxonomicName>
have not yet been thoroughly examined. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
